{"tid":1481840,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"佢話冇咗熱情 冇信心可以同我行落去","createTime":"2019-08-18T01:01:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T02:57:20.000Z","uid":176601,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"98c77f697cd1bea84e62a002abea627c8f99554e","tid":1481840,"uid":176601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T01:01:27.000Z","msg":"同佢一齊咗年幾 佢話同我冇共同興趣 對呢段感情冇咗熱情 我地有一齊傾過點樣解決個問題 大家都有共識 就係一齊去試下做啲新活動 例如瑜珈 羽毛球等等啦 <br />\n<br />\n我地都plan咗幾時去做呢啲活動 而佢喺實行呢啲計劃之前就同我講 話佢已經冇動力去做 冇信心去試 話要冷靜下<br />\n<br />\n呢家我地喺冷靜期 而我個諗法係我其實仲愛佢 不過我已經有心理準備要分手 因為我已經感受唔到佢嘅愛<br />\n<br />\n我應該等個完咗冷靜期先真正分手定提早講分手 唔好浪費時間？"},{"pid":"5c9848a2243fb96a7d38118a08cd1fcb1c88b7ed","tid":1481840,"uid":176601,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T01:02:19.000Z","msg":"Btw 今日維園見呀！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"0a3b4a1055f1d95ada4db40b1e3c95cfa954b7bb","tid":1481840,"uid":176601,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T01:57:37.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以理下我吖"},{"pid":"e13b45ebc65347ce29c446ae413cf50cd70412f9","tid":1481840,"uid":1525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T01:59:12.000Z","msg":"巴打 我係隔離post都有類似問題<br />\n<br />\n我係早啲stage 岩岩開始話淡話悶<br />\n仲未有解決方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db378e60bdd8ec8e4a94f4a03a6956c52d785cfa","tid":1481840,"uid":176601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e13b45ebc65347ce29c446ae413cf50cd70412f9","tid":1481840,"uid":1525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T01:59:12.000Z","msg":"巴打 我係隔離post都有類似問題<br />\n<br />\n我係早啲stage 岩岩開始話淡話悶<br />\n仲未有解決方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:01:32.000Z","msg":"我係絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢肯唔肯同你一齊試新嘢先？"},{"pid":"adf16019de64d8633aa5c08b87a73ef5d0568af5","tid":1481840,"uid":1525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e13b45ebc65347ce29c446ae